便得多了<br />\n每隻視力不佳的蛇都可以受惠了<br />\n而科學家有望研發一些蛇類的隱形眼鏡<br />\n以配合佢地本身嘅習性<br />\n係可見嘅將來 眼鏡蛇嘅稱號可能將要消失了<br />\n（好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"937a2a87409c1dbf00e0389355371910889d3e5d","tid":396443,"uid":58604,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:13:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未有眼鏡之前啲蛇會點啲水珠係隻眼度<br />\n用意就係形成lens<br />\n類似人類嘅隱形眼鏡<br />\n但咁樣啲水珠成日蒸發<br />\n或者俾自己吸收左 太煩了<br />\n後尾人類發明左眼鏡就方便得多了<br />\n每隻視力不佳的蛇都可以受惠了<br />\n而科學家有望研發一些蛇類的隱形眼鏡<br />\n以配合佢地本身嘅習性<br />\n係可見嘅將來 眼鏡蛇嘅稱號可能將要消失了<br />\n（好似係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）</blockquote><br />\n紅字為笑點"},{"pid":"422ca2198d41dab11cd7fb9a438b4ea5ef761bde","tid":396443,"uid":32486,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:14:18.000Z","msg":"未有溥儀之前<br />\n溥儀眼鏡叫咩"},{"pid":"4e72e9ea9415fa4efa0be92175fd84beaa40ed84","tid":396443,"uid":33643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:16:33.000Z","msg":"飯鏟頭"},{"pid":"2d14bcdab7a7865febc286f00963c889d2db100b","tid":396443,"uid":17878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:17:11.000Z","msg":"膨頸蛇"},{"pid":"0191c18c2d2329346801c52a5783b54727c2a259","tid":396443,"uid":31254,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:17:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>未有溥儀之前<br />\n溥儀眼鏡叫咩</blockquote><br />\n光緒眼鏡"},{"pid":"d47d32d34ee35e9f791d8e15273efb0d68df373c","tid":396443,"uid":122540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:20:20.000Z","msg":"咩呀，眼鏡蛇係眼鏡牌子黎"},{"pid":"bf1ccf08b15dc76eba02ba165a851d96803aa6ee","tid":396443,"uid":68098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-12T01:23:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n飯鏟頭<i